            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>pine nut & seed mix </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and golden</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p><p>Once toasted, remove from the pan and set aside for later</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1630512523635-x200.jpg",
